unittitle_ssm: International Association of Bridge, Structural and Ornamental Iron Workers, Local 197 Records
abstract_ssm: The Stone Derrickmen and Riggers Association, Local 197 of New York, NY was granted its Charter by the International Association of Bridge, Structural, Ornamental and Reinforcing Iron Workers on September 16, 1916. The collection consists of financial and annual reports, publications, correspondence, meeting minutes, contracts and photographs of Local 197. Reproductions of the founding Charter of Local 197 as well as early editions of the Bridgeman and Ironworkers magazine are also included. Approximately forty-five black and white photographs document construction projects throughout New York City from 1902 until the early 1990s.
